rking with the very same individuals but as we begin introducing the powerful resources that we will put to work for your account you will see an increase in the level of insight and support when new beer brands are added to our awardwinning portfolio you will also have the opportunity to attract new customers and create an even richer beer experience in your location learn how we have perfected the acquisition and integration process in this insightful video account growth our beer portfolio consists of over  of the world’s best beer brands it spans across the board in terms of country of origin size and geography of brewer style taste and consumer diversity with the power of this portfolio we are confident that we can help your account become a true beer destination – a place where customers can find the beers they love and new ones that might appeal to their tastes best of all our portfolio continues to growthe right way we’re not brand collectors but we are committed to partnering with beer brands that are the best in their category giving you and your customers a wide array of options here you’ll learn more about our awardwinning portfolio service and execution excellence we know that the quality of service and execution that we provide in the beer delivery process has a huge impact on your ability to be profitable as you will see in this video we not only have indepth consumer market and beer expertise but also the enormous logistical resources that it takes to ensure a consistently high level of execution the bottom line is that we are good at getting beer into your account with frequency and quality while providing your customers with a truly unforgettable beer experience every time they walk through your door collaborative partnerships we strive to be your true partner in the beer business to this end we’ve invested heavily in a number of resources that go far beyond what it takes to simply deliver beer our vast research resources are designed to help you k