 a week operation for hazen watching hazen run the brewery is a little like watching willy wonka run the chocolate factory when i visit him during a bottling day hazen runs between the bottling line and the packaging supplies in a hurried yet methodical manner he stands up bottles on the line starts the machine slides his way across the brewhouse to the packaging materials and hand assembles the sixpacks that will hold the soontobe bottled beer andrews beer is straightforward unassuming and entirely enjoyable his product line includes the st nick porter the northern brown ale the english pale ale and the summer seasonal rubys golden ale a celebration of the amarillo hop hazens english pale ale is a delightfully balanced product that neither over or underwhelms the palate from beerscribecom established  website httpmainebrewersguildorgbrewersandrewsbrewingcompany is this your brewery were working on some great new features for breweries get started and claim this brewery micro brewery  high st lincolnville maine  us hours of operation mon am  pm tue am  pm wed am  pm thu am  pm fri am  pm sat am  am mon  fri  am   pm sat  am   am contact location    location website location opened in  discover nearby breweries wanna know what is nearby andrews brewing company brewerymap can tell you everything you need to know map nearby breweries × modal header submit changes for review close helpful links terms of use disclaimer privacy policy built for developers brewerydb was made by developers for developers our vast collection of data can be accessed via our free api start developing for free connect with brewerydb steadyserv steadyserv feedbacksteadyservcom   steadyserv technologies llc andrew beers  tableau software inc  email vice president product development  tableausoftwarecom  phone    business card for andrew beers andrew beers vice president product development seattle wa areaemail avail  day free trial tableau software inc  n th st ste  seattle wa  tel   wwwtableauso