wynwood brewing  use of the term craft brew  see also  references company historyedit the company was formed on july   with the merger of redhook ale brewery and widmer brothers brewery cba acquired kona brewing company on october   in  cba launched a new brand called omission beer promoting the beer as specially crafted to remove gluten in  cba launched a cider  square mile cider and in  entered into a partnership with the chive to create kcco beer under the independentchiveowned resignation brewery moniker the company was originally named craft brewers alliance but changed its name to craft brew alliance on january   as of march   craft brew alliance is publicly traded as nasdaq brew prior to this date it was publicly traded as hook productsedit the company produces brands such as redhook widmer brothers brewing omission beer and several others officers and directorsedit name title kurt r widmer chairman emeritus andrew j thomas chief executive officer joe vanderstelt chief financial officer treasurer scott mennen chief operating officer john glick vp emerging business dan partelow vp commercial development peter schauf vp international sales derek hahm vp sales  brewpubs matt abraham chief information officer ken kunze chief marketing officer on november   the company announced that effective january   andy thomas will take over as the company’s new ceo on may   cba announced the appointment of joe vandersteldt to cfo along with several other changes at the executive leadership level redhookedit redhook was founded in the early s in seattle at first the brewery was a small shop in the seattle neighborhood of ballard the beers brewed by redhook include esb ipa pilsner copperhook and seasonal brews widmer brothers brewingedit widmer brothers brews various beers including drifter pale ale nelson imperial ipa rotator ipa series drop top amber ale pitch black ipa and upheaval ipa kona brewing companyedit the kona brewing company was founded in the spring of  and is hawaiis largest brewery omission beeredit the companys omission beer is designed to have low gluten content by using a proprietary enzyme to remove gluten from traditional beer ingredients  namely malted barley square mile cider companyedit launched in  there are two primary products under this brand  the original which is a traditional hard apple cider and spur  vine which is a hopped apple cider appalachian mountain breweryedit on december   cba entered into a strategic partnership agreement with boone ncbased appalachian mountain brewery amb as part of the partnership cba will act as master distributor for amb allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network cba has taken an undisclosed minority stake in amb cisco brewers incedit on september   cba announced a strategic partnership agreement with nantucketbased cisco brewers as with previous partner amb cba will act as master distributor for amb allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network cba has taken an undisclosed minority stake in cisco brewers wynwood brewingedit on december   cba announced a strategic partnership agreement with miami flbased wynwood brewing cba is taking a  stake in wynwood valuing the deal at under  million as with previous partners amb and cisco brewers cba will act as master distributor for wynwood allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network use of the term craft brewedit while the company name contains the phrase craft brew it does not meet the definition of a craft brewer according to the brewers association due to the percentage stake owned by anheuserbusch inbev the brewers association defines american craft brewers as small independent and traditional with small defined as an annual production of  million barrels of beer or less a limit changed in  from  million to  million to ensure the ongoing inclusion of boston beer company the producer of the samuel adams brand independent defined as at least  owned or controlled by a craft brewer and traditional defined as at least  of its volume being all malt beer see alsoedit portals access related topics beer portal companies portal referencesedit notes  a b craft brew alliance inc annual report for the fiscal year ended december    brewers association releases top  breweries of  brewers association april    a b c  craft beers that arent the street january    a b craft brewers alliance inc form k us sec p  as of december   ab owns approximately  of our outstanding common stock and under the exchange agreement has the right to appoint two designees to our board of directors and to observe the conduct of all standing board committees   reimer miriam  august  anheuserbusch takeover target craft brewers alliance thestreet retrieved  august    craft brewers alliance accessed   postmerger widmer reports profit portland business journal august    craft brew alliance reports second quarter  results craft brew alliance official web site  craft brewers alliance is now craft brew alliance  craft brew alliance changes ticker symbol to brew accessed january    a b c brands of company accessed oct    key people in cba  next ceo for cba  andy thomas  craft brew alliance inc brewo key developments reuterscom retrieved    craft brew alliance inc brewo people reuterscom retrieved    drinking is believing  faq omission beer  retrieved    appalachian mountain brewery appalachian mountain brewery appalachian mountain brewery retrieved    craft brew alliance cisco brewers craft brew alliance retrieved    brewbound wynwood brewing brewbound retrieved    a b craft brewer defined brewersassociationorg retrieved    that craft beer youre drinking isnt craft beer – do you care time business  money august    report the craft beer industrys big year associations now march    a b brewers association craft beer is now a  billion category brewbound march     craft beers that arent thestreetcom retrieved   v t e anheuserbusch inbev co