into a strategic partnership agreement with boone ncbased appalachian mountain brewery amb as part of the partnership cba will act as master distributor for amb allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network cba has taken an undisclosed minority stake in amb cisco brewers incedit on september   cba announced a strategic partnership agreement with nantucketbased cisco brewers as with previous partner amb cba will act as master distributor for amb allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network cba has taken an undisclosed minority stake in cisco brewers wynwood brewingedit on december   cba announced a strategic partnership agreement with miami flbased wynwood brewing cba is taking a  stake in wynwood valuing the deal at under  million as with previous partners amb and cisco brewers cba will act as master distributor for wynwood allowing their products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network use of the term craft brewedit while the company name contains the phrase craft brew it does not meet the definition of a craft brewer according to the brewers association due to the percentage stake owned by anheuserbusch inbev the brewers association defines american craft brewers as small independent and traditional with small defined as an annual production of  million barrels of beer or less a limit changed in  from  million to  million to ensure the ongoing inclusion of boston beer company the producer of the samuel adams brand independent defined as at least  owned or controlled by a craft brewer and traditional defined as at least  of its volume being all malt beer see alsoedit portals access related topics beer portal companies portal referencesedit notes  a b craft brew alliance inc annual report for the fiscal year ended december    brewers association releases top  breweries of  brewers association april    a b c  craft beers that arent the street january    a b craft brewers alliance inc