eir products to ship via the anheuserbusch inbev distributor network use of the term craft brewedit while the company name contains the phrase craft brew it does not meet the definition of a craft brewer according to the brewers association due to the percentage stake owned by anheuserbusch inbev the brewers association defines american craft brewers as small independent and traditional with small defined as an annual production of  million barrels of beer or less a limit changed in  from  million to  million to ensure the ongoing inclusion of boston beer company the producer of the samuel adams brand independent defined as at least  owned or controlled by a craft brewer and traditional defined as at least  of its volume being all malt beer see alsoedit portals access related topics beer portal companies portal referencesedit notes  a b craft brew alliance inc annual report for the fiscal year ended december    brewers association releases top  breweries of  brewers association april    a b c  craft beers that arent the street january    a b craft brewers alliance inc form k us sec p  as of december   ab owns approximately  of our outstanding common stock and under the exchange agreement has the right to appoint two designees to our board of directors and to observe the conduct of all standing board committees   reimer miriam  august  anheuserbusch takeover target craft brewers alliance thestreet retrieved  august    craft brewers alliance accessed   postmerger widmer reports profit portland business journal august    craft brew alliance reports second quarter  results craft brew alliance official web site  craft brewers alliance is now craft brew alliance  craft brew alliance changes ticker symbol to brew accessed january    a b c brands of company accessed oct    key people in cba  next ceo for cba  andy thomas  craft brew alliance inc brewo key developments reuterscom retrieved    craft brew alliance inc brewo people reuterscom retrieved    drinking is believing 